{"tid":1778410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雲海：立法會批了興建海水化淡廠 不過同時提議每年用48億買東江水直至2040！","createTime":"2019-12-11T02:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:50:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2a7e7c118d64790e4789d55b07bf725522c35b","tid":1778410,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:45:01.000Z","msg":"當今日焦點大家討論緊兩電加價，我想提返醒所有市民，水務署上個月極度低調咁公布咗一份「全面水資源管理策略」報告(份報告可以喺水務署網頁睇晒）當中政府係提議香港繼續購買極昂貴嘅東江水直至2040年！淨係呢個日期已經好吊詭！即係仲差七年就變一國一制嘅時候先再同大陸傾呀？！而且仲要講到明已經喺11月立法會成功撥出77億喺將軍澳興建海水化淡廠，只不過係建後備用，而我哋香港繼續要花公帑每年比48億去買東江水！其實我覺得成件事係比兩電加價更加值得關注！但上個月政府透過水務署公布呢份報告時，唔搞任何記者招待會、唔發新聞稿，就係想大家市民繼續做豬！不過我都相信絕大部份都係豬！我講完都嘥氣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/3305096766199101?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197517173623758%2Fposts%2F3305096766199101%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=49cc8bf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/3305096766199101?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e7cb8446cd7e38d9cad06809909ade8bb2aee350","tid":1778410,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"blocked<br />\n邊個post 分化狗block邊個"},{"pid":"4aadc55103a9f5e30f12e4a3c07e38bacc2e084d","tid":1778410,"uid":100133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d5f868ff4073a0802431bce35ea764cc7f3b8f","tid":1778410,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=